OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FAn electrician who stabbed a judge's
OL,7,Fdaughter to death in a frenzied rage
OL,8,Fbefore blowing up their home in a gas
OL,9,Fexplosion is set to be sentenced for
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FClifton George, 45, killed his partner
OL,13,FAnnabel Rook, 46, by stabbing her 31
OL,14,Ftimes during a row at their east
OL,15,FLondon home after she had said they
OL,16,Fshould end their 10-year relationship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
