PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FIn the aftermath of the killing,
OL,7,FGeorge started a fire in the basement
OL,8,Fin order to cause a gas canister
OL,9,Fexplosion which ripped through the
OL,10,Fhouse.
OL,12,FGeorge denied murder at a Snaresbrook
OL,13,FCrown Court trial, but was convicted
OL,14,Fby a jury last week and will receive a
OL,15,Flife sentence from Mr Justice
OL,16,FConstable KC on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
