PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FHis attempt to claim loss of self
OL,7,Fcontrol as a partial defence fell
OL,8,Fapart during the trial, after jurors
OL,9,Fheard evidence of his short fuse,
OL,10,Fangry outbursts at Ms Rook, and at
OL,11,Fleast one incident when he had been
OL,12,Fviolent towards her.
OL,14,FMs Rook, a charity worker who co-
OL,15,Ffounded social enterprise MamaSuze to
OL,16,Fhelp refugees through arts workshops,
OL,17,Fis the daughter of retired Old Bailey
OL,18,Fjudge Peter Rook.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
