OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FShe was punched, throttled, and then
OL,7,Fstabbed by George at their home in
OL,8,FDumont Road, Stoke Newington, on the
OL,9,Fnight of June 16 last year.
OL,11,FIn the aftermath of the murder, George
OL,12,Ftriggered the gas explosion ` likened
OL,13,Fby neighbours to an "mini earthquake"
OL,14,F` which ripped through the property
OL,15,Fand blew off part of the roof.
OL,17,FGeorge was found lying on the kitchen
OL,18,Ffloor covered in blood and then tried
OL,19,Fto stab himself with a shard of broken
OL,20,Fglass while Ms Rook lay dead in the
OL,21,Fliving room.
OL,26,@uD@UOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
