OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FMs Davin said her friend had
OL,7,Facknowledged by summer 2024 that the
OL,8,Frelationship was "abusive" and a
OL,9,Fcouple of weeks before her death Ms
OL,10,FRook left her sister a message saying
OL,11,Fthe relationship was "not tenable".
OL,13,F"I fear there will be some more wrath
OL,14,Fto come," she said, but she went on to
OL,15,Fpredict they would "get through this
OL,16,Fand will be stronger for it out the
OL,17,Fother side".
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@ZO]sD@VOUsD@bO]uD@AOUvD@IO]wD@
OL,26,ATOUyD@KO]
