OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FBefore the fatal stabbing, Ms Rook had
OL,7,Ftold George that they should separate
OL,8,Fand he should move out of their home,
OL,9,Fwhich she owned.
OL,11,F"In the course of that argument he
OL,12,Fpunched her, he then tried to strangle
OL,13,Fher, and then he went to the kitchen
OL,14,Fto get a knife, he came back with the
OL,15,Fknife and he stabbed her to death,"
OL,16,Fsaid prosecutor William Emlyn Jones KC.
OL,18,F"He lost his temper, and in his rage
OL,19,Fhe murdered Annabel."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@cO]zD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
