PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,FGeorge, who had been drinking red wine
OL,7,Fthat night, tried to paint Ms Rook as
OL,8,Fthe abuser in the relationship,
OL,9,Fdespite "overwhelming" evidence that
OL,10,Fhe was controlling and volatile.
OL,12,FFollowing the guilty verdict, CPS
OL,13,Fprosecutor Catherine Gould said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with the family and loved
OL,15,Fones of Annabel Rook.
OL,17,F"It is devastating that her life was
OL,18,Ftaken in such a violent manner in her
OL,19,Fown home by someone she should have
OL,20,Fbeen able to trust.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@VO]uD@bOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
