PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780974217
OL,3,CElectrician faces life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurdering judge's daughter in a rage
OL,6,F"We worked closely with the police to
OL,7,Fbuild the strongest possible case and
OL,8,Fto deliver justice for Annabel.
OL,10,F"We know that nothing can replace
OL,11,FAnnabel but hope that this verdict can
OL,12,Fbring some small measure of comfort to
OL,13,Fthose who knew and loved her."
OL,15,FGeorge will be sentenced to life in
OL,16,Fprison, with the judge set to
OL,17,Fdetermine what minimum term he should
OL,18,Fserve before being eligible for
OL,19,Frelease.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@^O]
